<%- include('../partials/header', { title: 'Nature Reset' }) %>

<main>
  <!-- Journey Hero -->
  <section class="journey-hero section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="journey-hero-label">3-5 days</p>
      <h1>Nature Reset</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Mountains and coast around Rio</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Opening -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <p class="journey-opening">Nature in Brazil doesn't sit far away.</p>
        <p>Around Rio, it's close and varied, from mountains and waterfalls to coastline and islands.</p>
        <p>This experience is designed to take you out of the intensity of the city and into that space.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What This Is -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>What This Is</h2>
        <p>This is not one fixed place.</p>
        <p>It's a nature-based experience shaped around locations near Rio, depending on what you need.</p>
        <p>This may include:</p>
        <ul class="journey-list">
          <li>The mountains (Teresopolis, Petropolis)</li>
          <li>The south coast (Paraty, Ilha Grande)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I Take Care Of / What You Experience -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-two-col">
        <div>
          <h2>What I Take Care Of</h2>
          <ul class="journey-list">
            <li>Choosing the right location based on your intention</li>
            <li>Safe, comfortable accommodation</li>
            <li>Transport and movement between places</li>
            <li>A simple structure, without overfilling your time</li>
            <li>Optional activities, without pressure</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>What You Experience</h2>
          <ul class="journey-list">
            <li>Time in nature that feels present</li>
            <li>Slower mornings and unstructured afternoons</li>
            <li>Water, forest and open space</li>
          </ul>
          <h4 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-forest);">In Paraty or Ilha Grande</h4>
          <ul class="journey-list">
            <li>The sea, in a quieter setting</li>
            <li>Movement between water and land</li>
          </ul>
          <h4 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-forest);">In the Mountains</h4>
          <ul class="journey-list">
            <li>Cooler air, silence and distance from the city</li>
            <li>Walking, stillness and space</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Difference -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>The Difference</h2>
        <p>Most nature trips are rushed or disconnected.</p>
        <p>I design this so it feels intentional and aligned with what you need.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who This Is For -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>Who This Is For</h2>
        <ul class="journey-list">
          <li>You need a reset</li>
          <li>You want nature without logistical stress</li>
          <li>You're travelling alone but want support</li>
          <li>You want space, but not isolation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Changes -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>What Changes</h2>
        <p>Your pace slows.<br>Your attention returns.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="included-section">
        <div class="included-list">
          <h3>Your Investment Covers</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>3-5 nights of carefully selected accommodation</li>
            <li>Meals throughout your stay</li>
            <li>Internal transportation</li>
            <li>All planned experiences and activities</li>
            <li>My guidance throughout the journey</li>
            <li>Local connections and introductions</li>
            <li>Pre-trip planning and customisation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="included-list">
          <h3>Not Included</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>International flights to/from Brazil</li>
            <li>Travel insurance (required)</li>
            <li>Personal shopping and souvenirs</li>
            <li>Visa fees if applicable</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--color-warm-gray); font-size: 0.95rem;">I'm happy to advise on flight options and help with any logistics. Just ask.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>How We Begin</h2>
        <p>We start with a conversation. From there, I shape the experience around you.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Start the Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
